-Ls95cNsxspki-yHJbrq.description: The hotel was solidly built in three phases; The front half was constructed in 1996, the back half in 2001, and the pool and patio area, in 2010. All rooms have A/C, direct dial phones with free international and local calls, coffee makers, a small writing table and chairs, a closet and dresser, and an in-room safe. There are three suites which have in-bath Jacuzzis, microwaves and a small fridge.  There is a sixty person bar and restaurant, and a big two story solarium room with a large Mayan waterfall aquarium, a solar-heated Jacuzzi beside the new pool, a computer station with four computers for people without a laptop, and a new fully equipped gym.  The location is multi-purpose. It is ideal for first and last night stays in Costa Rica for tourists and condo owners, as well as being conveniently located directly across the street from the New Convention Center.

-Lv7bB4SD1Jt38_Z7tV1.description:
The Resort Estate at Cariari offers a grand home featuring a central courtyard With a swimming pool, six bedrooms and multiple social areas this is a home carefully designed to live, enjoy and share, with additional independent office and lounge area, a tennis court and a lap pool. The L-shaped 3-acre property has a wonderful location in Cariari, less than 20 minutes away from the international airport and near Class A offices, international schools, and the nearby Cariari Country Club and golf course.

The extensive Resort Estate in Cariari has a private driveway access with palm trees at either side, preceded by a guard house protecting the main entrance. An imposing yet elegant architecture greets you onto the covered entrance and into the foyer. Right in front, the central courtyard displays its natural lighting and fresh ambience into each space. This is a rectangular area boasting an open distribution and surrounded by arched windows with a soothing fountain in the middle.

-LybctlquEJZTAvyhGs-.description:
The Cariari Collection Estate, a warm blend of 19th century elegance and 21st century convenience. This two-level home boasts double height ceilings with marble floors and large open areas and that characterize an inviting architectural design. The unique social area is a focal point and grand feature of the house, offering a roofed swimming pool, gym, home theater and a game room in an upper level. The large 4,169m2 property offers private yet open living in Cariari, minutes from the airport with easy access to the highway, schools, and the nearby golf course.

The first impression of The Cariari Collection Estate begins with a brick driveway inside a massive and fully enclosed property with landscaped gardens. A delicately shaped fountain greets you to the main entrance, surrounded by several round Roman columns with palm trees that highlight the home’s ever-present elegance and symmetry. Up three marble stairs, two large wooden doors open onto the main foyer.
